race.comment: DEL MAR JESSIE (7) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 2.25 lengths at this track in a handy 21.42 beating QWERTY. Winner at her latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Can measure up again. QWERTY (2) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame from Box 1 last run (21.59) at this track. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Hard to beat again. MAXIMUS WILL (8) comes off an average effort last start when fifth at this track over 375m behind DEL MAR JESSIE (22.06) in a Grade 3/4. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. One of the main contenders. WHO KNOWS (1) has a solid strike rate from this box.
